复杂连接词

Variery is more important than accuracy 

Although
- so that -


Prompt
	The government should tax sugary drinks.



Although 
	Although sugary drinks are popular among consumers, the government should tax them.

In order to
	The government should impose a tax on sugar-sweetened beverages in order to curb excessive sugar consumption.

as a means of
	The government should impose a tax on sugar-sweetened beverages as a means of improving public health.

so that 
	The government should tax sugary drinks so that people consume less sugar.